Class SetOntologyIDData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.owlapi.change.OWLOntologyChangeData
      • org.semanticweb.owlapi.change.SetOntologyIDData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, HasSignature

    public final class SetOntologyIDData
extends OWLOntologyChangeData
    Represents the specific non-ontology data required by a SetOntologyID change.
    Instances of this class are immutable.
    Since:
    3.5
    Author:
    Matthew Horridge, Stanford University, Bio-Medical Informatics Research Group, Date: 27/04/2012
